data.description:
This spacious ranch house boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, and 2 half bathrooms, offering a perfect blend of comfort and convenience for main level living. If you're someone who enjoys hosting gatherings, this house is an absolute gem. The two adjacent living spaces, complemented by a generously sized kitchen dining area featuring sleek granite countertops, provide an ideal setting for entertaining guests. Additionally, there's a versatile room off the living room that can serve as either an office or a non-conforming bedroom, catering to your specific needs. House is being sold as-is.

The bedrooms are notably spacious, ensuring ample room for relaxation and personalization. The highlight of the house is undoubtedly the large 5-piece bathroom, complete with a luxurious jetted tub, offering a serene escape for relaxation and rejuvenation.

The basement presents an exciting opportunity for expansion, with partially framed walls and a convenient half bathroom already in place. Moreover, the property offers an oversized two-car detached garage, perfectly accommodating your parking needs, along with additional parking available in the driveway.
